#. type: itemize
#: ../texi/tramp.texi:5571
msgid ""
"If you find the cleanup disturbing, because the file names in @code{recentf-"
"list} are precious to you, you could add the following two forms in your "
"@file{~/.emacs} after loading the @code{tramp} and @code{recentf} packages:"
